<inglise> COMMISSION DECISION of 12 February 1997 defining the treatment of the income of undertakings for collective investment (UCIs) for the purpose of the implementation of Council Directive 89/130/EEC, Euratom on the harmonization of the compilation of gross national product at market prices (Text with EEA relevance) (97/157/EC, Euratom) </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI OTSUS, millega m&auml;&auml;ratletakse &uuml;hisinvesteerimisettev&otilde;tjate (&Uuml;IE) tulu k&auml;sitlemine rahvamajanduse kogutoodangu turuhindades arvutamise &uuml;htlustamist k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu direktiivi 89/130/EM&Uuml;, Euratom artikli 1 rakendamiseks 12. veebruar 1997 (EMPs kohaldatav tekst) </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> (97/157/E&Uuml;, Euratom) EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Atomic Energy Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Aatomienergia&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Directive 89/130/EEC, Euratom of 13 February 1989 on the harmonization of the compilation of gross national product at market prices (1), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 13. veebruari 1989. aasta direktiivi 89/130/EM&Uuml;, Euratom rahvamajanduse kogutoodangu turuhindades arvutamise &uuml;htlustamise kohta (1) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas for the purpose of the definition of gross national product at market prices (GNPmp) pursuant to Article 1 of Directive 89/130/EEC, Euratom, which, in virtue of Article 8 (1) of Council Regulation (EC) No 2223/96 of 25 June 1996 on the European system of national and regional accounts in the Community (2), is applicable while Decision 94/728/EC, Euratom (3) remains in force, it is necessary to clarify the treatment of the income of undertakings for collective investment (UCIs) according to the European system of integrated economic accounts (ESA) in force; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: turuhindades arvutatava rahvamajanduse kogutoodangu (RKTth) m&auml;&auml;ratlemiseks direktiivi 89/130/EM&Uuml;, Euratom artikli 1 kohaselt, mida kohaldatakse Euroopa rahvamajanduse ja regionaalse arvepidamise s&uuml;steemi k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu 25. juuni 1996. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2223/96 (2) artikli 8 l&otilde;ike 1 p&otilde;hjal seni, kuni otsus 94/728/E&Uuml;, Euratom (3) kehtib, on vaja selgitada &uuml;hisinvesteerimisettev&otilde;tjate (&Uuml;IE) tulu k&auml;sitlemist kehtiva Euroopa rahvamajanduse arvepidamise s&uuml;steemi (ESA) kohaselt; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the ESA second edition does not contain explicit provisions for the recording of the income of UCIs, in particular their undistributed income; </inglise>
<eesti> ESA teine v&auml;ljaanne ei sisalda selges&otilde;nalisi s&auml;tteid &Uuml;IEde tulu m&auml;rkimiseks, eelk&otilde;ige nende jaotamata tulu puhul; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is therefore necessary to interpret the rules of the ESA second edition, according to these underlying principles, in order to indicate a method of recording this income; </inglise>
<eesti> seet&otilde;ttu on vaja t&otilde;lgendada ESA teise v&auml;ljaande reegleid nende alusp&otilde;him&otilde;tete kohaselt, et m&auml;&auml;rata sellise tulu kirjendamise meetod; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Decision are in accordance with the opinion of the Committee established by Article 6 of Directive 89/130/EEC, Euratom, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas otsuses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las direktiivi 89/130/EM&Uuml;, Euratom artikli 6 alusel asutatud komitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS DECISION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA OTSUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purpose of the implementation of Directive 89/130/EEC, Euratom, the UCIs' income consists of the interest received on the deposits and other investments acquired on the one hand, and of the dividends earned on the shares held by the UCIs, on the other. </inglise>
<eesti> Direktiivi 89/130/EM&Uuml;, Euratom rakendamisel koosneb &Uuml;IEde tulu &uuml;helt poolt hoiustelt ja muudelt investeeringutelt saadud intressidest ja teiselt poolt &Uuml;IEde omatavatelt aktsiatelt teenitud dividendidelt. </eesti>
<inglise> These interest and dividends may be paid out to investors, or added to the capital. </inglise>
<eesti> Need intressid ja dividendid v&otilde;ib maksta investoritele v&otilde;i lisada kapitalile. </eesti>
<inglise> When distributed, this income is recorded in the Distribution of income account of the shareholders, within property and entrepreneurial income (Code R40 of the ESA, currently in force). </inglise>
<eesti> Jaotamise korral kirjendatakse see tulu aktsion&auml;ride tulujaotuskontole tuluna varalt ja ettev&otilde;tlusest (kehtiva ESA kood R 40). </eesti>
<inglise> When this income is not distributed, it must be treated as an income paid out by the UCI to its shareholders, which the latter reinvest immediately in the UCI. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui seda tulu ei jaotata, tuleb seda k&auml;sitleda tuluna, mida &Uuml;IE maksab oma aktsion&auml;ridele ja mille viimased investeerivad kohe uuesti &Uuml;IEsse. </eesti>
<inglise> This means that this income must be recorded within property and entrepreneurial income like in the case of distributed income. </inglise>
<eesti> See t&auml;hendab, et see tulu tuleb kirjendada varalt ja ettev&otilde;tlusest saadava tuluna nagu jaotatava tulu puhul. </eesti>
<inglise> Moreover, the same amount will be classified as part of shares, in the Financial account of the shareholders. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisaks sellele kirjendatakse seesama summa aktsion&auml;ride finantskontole aktsiatena. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision is addressed to the Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev otsus on adresseeritud liikmesriikidele. Br&uuml;ssel, 12. veebruar 1997 </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 12 February 1997. </inglise>
